{"tid":966673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當地人好nice㗎！ 獲招待茶水疑被下藥　華女獨遊印度慘遭迷姦","createTime":"2019-01-03T03:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T05:28:37.000Z","uid":72009,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"85aeefc334587d647edb68b549a2b47166c2f5fc","tid":966673,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:31:43.000Z","msg":"中國貴州一名25歲女子獨自在印度中央邦旅遊時，周一（12月31日）向當地警方報案，指自己遭當地一群青年下藥性侵。警方表示，警方已立理此案並展開調查，已要求該女子進行醫學檢測。 <br />\n<br />\n該名女子報稱，自己在旅途中結識一群青年後，一度獲對方招待；惟她飲下對方提供的茶後，隨即失去意識，醒來後懷疑自己的茶被下藥，她亦遭到性侵。目前，警方正調查事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190103/mobile/bkn-20190103033144740-0103_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190103%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190103033144740-0103_00912_001.html&d=s782VIATokQK7aLWwCtuW7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=b8d1751a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190103/mobile/bkn-20190103033144740-0103_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n應該起碼俾一打人插過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef05a25325347c096264096e74c5e66b4d5ac20","tid":966673,"uid":46933,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"無殺埋已經好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048e119be7fcefa6251e81f5c4684171a13ead70","tid":966673,"uid":154738,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"醫學檢測又黎多獲"},{"pid":"9eeb06304e5dda6748e894de148d9a3d959727ef","tid":966673,"uid":55924,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:39:08.000Z","msg":"印度人好nice"},{"pid":"ffa8287a6fd4dfb7b676b2f33339099435041aa7","tid":966673,"uid":154570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:40:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c4f78d6f0eee80ffae46c70f4e6bed853871a56","tid":966673,"uid":150347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply